name: Jay Cunningham
text:
Hi Everyone 👋🏾
I genuinely appreciate the effort to ensure that students remain engaged and are still presented opportunity in leui of the conference being postponed. I wanted to take a moment and share opportunities for graduate school.

I'm a PhD student in Human Centered Design and Engineering at the University of Washington. I was planning to attend NSBE to share information about our amazing programs in UW. HCDE is an interdisciplinary engineering discipline that combines passion for people, technology, psychology, and design to create some of tomorrow's most innovative products. Our department has Certificate, MS, and PhD programs and are always seeking talented students of color to join our dynamic community. 
You can find more information at HCDE.UW.edu
Our department offers generous funding opportunities for MS and full funding for PhD students. We're also in partnership with programs like Louis Stokes, GEM, and more.
